OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784305119
OL,3,CFamily pays tribute to 'cheeky, funny
OL,4,Cand sassy' girl aged four, killed in
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe family of a four-year-old girl who
OL,8,Fwas killed in a crash in
OL,9,FNottinghamshire have paid tribute to
OL,10,Ftheir "cheeky, funny and sassy little
OL,11,Fgirl".
OL,13,FOlive Farrell was injured in a
OL,14,Fcollision on Sunday, 12 July, in
OL,15,FNottingham Road, in Gotham. She later
OL,16,Fdied in hospital.
OL,18,FA 59-year-old man was arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,20,Fdangerous driving and has been bailed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
