CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784305119
OL,3,CFamily pays tribute to 'cheeky, funny
OL,4,Cand sassy' girl aged four, killed in
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FA vigil will be held for Olive by her
OL,8,Ffamily and friends in Nottinghamshire
OL,9,Ftoday.
OL,11,FA written tribute from her family
OL,12,Freads: "Olive was a cheeky, funny and
OL,13,Fsassy little girl, who may have been
OL,14,Ftiny in size, but she certainly made
OL,15,Fup for it with her big personality.
OL,17,F"Not a day went by without Olive
OL,18,Fsinging and dancing her way round the
OL,19,Fhouse and spreading her affection;
OL,20,Falways kissing and cuddling and going
OL,21,Fout of her way to be kind to everyone.
OL,26,@tD@HOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
