CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784305119
OL,3,CFamily pays tribute to 'cheeky, funny
OL,4,Cand sassy' girl aged four, killed in
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"Olive's memory will live on with all
OL,8,Fthe colourful paintings we have around
OL,9,Fthe house. Quite often she would take
OL,10,Fherself off and come back with a
OL,11,Fbeautiful work of art as she was so
OL,12,Fcreative."
OL,14,FThey added that she was "inseparable"
OL,15,Ffrom her two brothers Teddy and Sonny,
OL,16,Fwhom she "looked up to with so much
OL,17,Flove".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@JO]vD@YOUvD@eO]xD@JOUyD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
