PN,34504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784305119
OL,3,CFamily pays tribute to 'cheeky, funny
OL,4,Cand sassy' girl aged four, killed in
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FOlive was due to join Sonny at primary
OL,8,Fschool. Her family say she was very
OL,9,Fexcited to be joining her brother
OL,10,Fthere.
OL,12,FThe statement reads: "No words can
OL,13,Fexpress the loss and pain felt across
OL,14,Fthe family and all that knew Olive, we
OL,15,Fare utterly devastated to think we can
OL,16,Fno longer hold her in our arms.
OL,26,@tD@VOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
