CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784305119
OL,3,CFamily pays tribute to 'cheeky, funny
OL,4,Cand sassy' girl aged four, killed in
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"We would like to thank the community
OL,8,Ffor coming together to support us
OL,9,Fthrough this difficult time. It has
OL,10,Fhelped greatly to see the outpouring
OL,11,Fof love with the messages and flowers
OL,12,Flaid on Nottingham Road."
OL,14,FNottinghamshire Police is appealing
OL,15,Ffor witnesses to come forward.
OL,17,FSergeant Paul Clark, from the force,
OL,18,Fsaid: "The circumstances of her death
OL,19,Fare being investigated, and we would
OL,20,Fask people not to speculate on social
OL,21,Fmedia.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@YO]
